  "3324650": {
    "name": "Kats Trigger",
    "steam_appid": 3324650,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Kats Trigger》是一款向1980年代至2020年代众多经典游戏、电影、漫画与动画作品致敬，并怀着对伟大创作者们的尊敬与敬意而制作的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验突破极限的超高速黑色动作，在紧张刺激的战斗之中，感受悄然展开的静谧故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/3e52f254de169abc7303e4c9e003f099.webp?t=1772144799\" width=615 height=51 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/ec5f791301f0cd9565d4ce44fdfe4ae5.poster.avif?t=1772144799\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/ec5f791301f0cd9565d4ce44fdfe4ae5.webm?t=1772144799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/ec5f791301f0cd9565d4ce44fdfe4ae5.mp4?t=1772144799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/71ea25537277e86044d432103ae55ced.poster.avif?t=1772144799\" width=616 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/71ea25537277e86044d432103ae55ced.webm?t=1772144799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/71ea25537277e86044d432103ae55ced.mp4?t=1772144799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 斩、射、刺、横扫一切。只要没有幸存者，这就是一次暗杀。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用正义之刃斩碎成群的敌人，用神圣的子弹惩戒远处狙击的卑劣之徒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以通过冲刺闪避敌人的攻击，也可以用刀弹开并进行反击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗讲究灵活的思考与非常规的行动，当然，最重要的是爽快感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/7a831ddec80ef06d3342c5dc62bcba41.webp?t=1772144799\" width=615 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/fc03e7e4e8393885dfdebfebd96c7e4e.poster.avif?t=1772144799\" width=440 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/fc03e7e4e8393885dfdebfebd96c7e4e.webm?t=1772144799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/fc03e7e4e8393885dfdebfebd96c7e4e.mp4?t=1772144799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 通过钢索进行的抓钩动作是本作的核心玩法之一。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将钢索钉入墙壁以实现高速移动，作用于特定物体以最大化机动性，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也可以对敌人使用，使其被束缚并失去战斗能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上下左右的立体自由移动，碾压敌人，尽情享受压倒性的速度感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/3c7d4e5be1aa4698a96618d8aece3bd4.webp?t=1772144799\" width=615 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/7c20b20e528eb87347eb069b93ed224d.poster.avif?t=1772144799\" width=616 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/7c20b20e528eb87347eb069b93ed224d.webm?t=1772144799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/7c20b20e528eb87347eb069b93ed224d.mp4?t=1772144799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 华丽的正面战斗并非唯一选择。有时，一次利落的挥刀就足够了。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >避开敌人的视线，悄然绕到背后，一击解决。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从背后发动攻击，杂兵会瞬间毙命，就连体型巨大的敌人也难以避免致命伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/1da274716d13142ddf8640eabba536b5.webp?t=1772144799\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/a95ef2f54c025b1ff02d4cca0f3d7279.poster.avif?t=1772144799\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/a95ef2f54c025b1ff02d4cca0f3d7279.webm?t=1772144799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/a95ef2f54c025b1ff02d4cca0f3d7279.mp4?t=1772144799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 使用多样化的武器，体验多样化的战斗。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战场各处可能会发现被人提前布置好的特殊弹药。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >近距离一击制敌的霰弹枪、专门破坏机械的导弹、焚烧大范围区域的火焰喷射器——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >善用各种弹药，让战斗更加有利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/99b1ae3183468588f373429840c3e481.webp?t=1772144799\" width=615 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/44803f29ab00f3416f4a7046e2b48f66.poster.avif?t=1772144799\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/44803f29ab00f3416f4a7046e2b48f66.webm?t=1772144799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/44803f29ab00f3416f4a7046e2b48f66.mp4?t=1772144799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ 敌人不只限于人类。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摧毁建筑一路追击的巨大拆除机械、统治天空的战斗机、用途不明而被改造的作物收割机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些如同“行走兵器”的巨大机械将作为首领登场，彻底改变战斗的规模。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324650/extras/67b13dc7de419de36bc945d38e5e5774.avif?t=1772144799\" width=800 height=410 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
